data.text:
Book a Famous Country Performer

The following roster of country performers offers a range of talent we can help you book for many types of events and functions. Whether you want a country performer for a corporate event or business party, tradeshow, appearance, and even a speaking engagement; or singers and bands for festivals like a fair and "concert in the park" music venues, to a political convention, a private party such as a birthday, wedding, or another major celebration - then CTI can be your celebrity booking agency when hiring a country performer listed below. If you are interested in a specific performer, click the name to read a full bio, see a price range of their booking fee, and then submit an inquiry to have a booking agent contact you.
